			<div>
				Originally Posted by <strong>Tinthalas Tigris</strong>
				<a href="showthread.php?s=2d19fc3219187a729da436fa87ee7f93&amp;p=1848621#post1848621" rel="nofollow"><img class="inlineimg" src="images/buttons/viewpost.gif" alt="View Post" /></a>
